text: Iqlas Naha (born 11 October 1994) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Puducherry in the 2018–19 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 19 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Puducherry cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
